messageBody:
amd64_hacker

You requested corrections to the poems you uploaded recently. I have
attached a pdf file with your original version in the left column and my
suggested changes in the right column in red. I put this in pdf format
since it maintains the QS letters without any problem (at least it
appears to.)

There are also some brief notes in blue at the bottom.

Hope you find this helpful, and it may be helpful to others who are
fairly new to QS.

Paige Gabhart
